Package: FRTCI
Type: Package
Title: Conduct the FRT CI Method of Ding, Feller, and Miratrix (2016, JRSS-B)
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2018-09-27
Authors@R: c(
  person("Ben", "Fifield", email = "benfifield@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  ) 
Description: This package implements methods developed by Ding, Feller, and Miratrix (2016)
    ''Randomization Inference for Treatment Effect Variation'', for validly testing
    whether there is unexplained variation in treatment effects across observations.
    The package includes wrapper functions implementing the proposed methods, as well
    as helper functions for analyzing and visualizing the results of the test.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports:
    quantreg,
    plyr,
    mvtnorm,
    foreach,
    parallel,
    doParallel
BugReports: https://github.com/bfifield/FRTCI/issues
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
